social_posts.post_text: #ad This Grammys season I’ve partnered with google pixel to share my pov as a creative working in music, through the lens of the pixel 7 camera features. I’m very honored to have been invited to attend this years Black Music Collective Grammys Honoree dinner. My creative life and career over nearly 13 years have been nurtured, supported, and so abundant solely because of the Black music community that has trusted me and believed in me to bring their visuals to life. No one has blessed me with more opportunities and freedom. My career truly would not be where it is today without my clients. I am eternally grateful. Gracias for a cutie night BMC & @googlepixel_us #teampixel #pixel7 #fixedonpixel

#Sponsored #TeamPixelTuesday As a creative director, it’s important that I have the time and space to conceptualize and manifest ideas for my artists and clients with full liberation. Your environment can be such a big influence on your imagination. We all have what I like to call our “factory settings”. It’s a type of routine or ritual that we do either when we start or perhaps end things. I still love to physically write things down, and print out my shot lists, however, being that I’m not a photographer - using the camera features on the Google Pixel such as Cinematic Blur, ultrawide camera, Photo Unblur, and the white balance settings actually help me see the photos or edits I see in my mind, in real-time, sort of like a preview. From ideation in-studio, to on-set for a shoot-day, my #pixel has become my latest digital tool to add into my process. Thank you #TeamPixel for allowing this analog girl into your digital world.

@youmatter Homecoming collection. You Matter is such a special brand c/o @demetriusharmon that I feel so honored to have worked with. A brand that provides educational opportunities and mental health support through scholarships and resources. You Matter is proof that you CAN use your online platform and influence to curate and build something for the community and for the people. Collection live now.
